  <h3>📌 Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

  <h5 class="mt-4">For Customers</h5>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>How do I book an appointment?</strong><br>
      Log into your portal, choose a business, pick a service, and select a time from the calendar.
    </li>
    <li><strong>Can I cancel or reschedule?</strong><br>
      Yes! Visit “My Appointments” and choose cancel or reschedule.
    </li>
    <li><strong>Do I need an account?</strong><br>
      Yes, creating an account keeps your bookings organized.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h5 class="mt-4">For Businesses</h5>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>How do I list services?</strong><br>
      Log in and navigate to your dashboard to add or manage services and availability.
    </li>
    <li><strong>How are bookings managed?</strong><br>
      View and respond to requests under “Pending Appointments.”
    </li>
    <li><strong>Can I sync calendars?</strong><br>
      Yes! Enable Google Calendar or iCal sync in settings.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h3>🛠️ Troubleshooting & Support</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>I forgot my password:</strong> Use the “Forgot Password?” link on the login page.</li>
    <li><strong>My calendar isn’t updating:</strong> Check that changes are saved and integrations are set.</li>
    <li><strong>I’m not receiving emails:</strong> Check spam or verify your email in profile settings.</li>
  </ul>

